title: Treasury Wine Estates to Buy U.S. and British Brands From Diageo
text:
Published By: NYTimes Int. Business - Yesterday 
The Australian winemaker will acquire labels such as Sterling Vineyard and Blossom Hill and other assets in a deal worth $552 million....
